MiEnRo stands as Minimal Enterprise Router

It is a Low Latency Dual Stack OpenRouter Software with L3 DDoS protection via BGP advertisements.

Using IEEE 802.1Q protocol on both interfaces the VLANs of wan port can be added, configured and deleted quickly with Linux tools without any configuration reload.

In normal working conditions the OpenBSD controller grants secure access to all devices including the same MiEnRo.

Before compiling xdp project, put this directory inside /usr/src/kernels/linux-$(uname -r | sed s/\-.*//).

mienroload - start Mienro
